animation_vocabulary:
  hit: brief recoil/stagger, use hurt face, recover to idle; never collapse
  death: separate collapse/downed state
  teleport: idle -> cyan particles -> vanish -> reappear; replaces old blink action
  slash: front arm leads, purple slash arc on front layer
  dash: cyan streaks behind character
